---
import TextBlurFading from '~/components/common/TextBlurFading';
import IntroScript  from './script';
---
<section class="sc-about__intro">
    <IntroScript client:visible={{ rootMargin: "100% 0% 100% 0%" }}/>
    <div class="about__intro">
        <div class="container grid">
            <p class="fs-24 about__intro-label">(Vision)</p>
            <div class="heading h4 cl-txt-title about__intro-vision-content">
                <span class="line"></span>
                <TextBlurFading
                    triggerOpts = {{
                        start: 'top top+=50%',
                        end: 'bottom top+=50%'
                    }}
                    client:visible={{ rootMargin: "100% 0% 100% 0%" }}
                    >
                    <p class="about__intro-vision-empty">|</p>As a designer and Rotarian, I believe in service above self. I believe being a designer is being a servant, in the most noble sense of the term; itâ€™s dedicating yourself to finding the right balance between user needs and business goals. I follow Design Thinking principles: metrics used to iterate fast and verify hypothesis. I believe in constant testing and fail fast, learn fast principles.
                </TextBlurFading>
                <span class="line"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container grid">
            <p class="fs-24 about__intro-label">(I work with)</p>
            <div class="about__intro-passion">
                <h3 class="heading h5 fw-med about__intro-passion-title">I have a strong passion for highly complex financial products</h3>
                <span class="line"></span>
                <div class="about__intro-passion-sub">
                    <p>I'm fascinated by their intricate details and the strategic thinking required to use them effectively. This drives me to stay updated on the latest developments in the financial industry.
                        <br/><br/>
                        <span class="cl-txt-disable">
                            if you are not a financial service.
                            <br/>
                            Sorry, I will not work for you.
                        </span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fw-med about__intro-passion-listing">
                <div class="about__intro-passion-circle">
                    <p class="fs-24 cl-txt-title about__intro-passion-circle-txt">Fintech</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about__intro-passion-circle">
                    <p class="fs-24 cl-txt-title about__intro-passion-circle-txt">Blockchain</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about__intro-passion-circle">
                    <p class="fs-24 cl-txt-title about__intro-passion-circle-txt">Web3</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style lang="scss">
    @use '~/assets/styles/mixins' as *;

    .sc-about__intro {}
    .about__intro {
        background-color: var(--cl-dm-bg);
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 4;
        &-label {
            grid-column: 1/3;
            padding-top: 12rem;
        }
        &-vision {
            &-content {
                grid-column: 4/17;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 12rem 0;
            }
            &-empty {
                width: 49rem;
                background-color: red;
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }
        &-passion {
            grid-column: 4/7;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            &-title {
                padding-top: 12rem;
                padding-bottom: 3.2rem;
            }
            &-sub {
                padding-top: 16.6rem;
            }
            &-listing {
                --circle-size: 50rem;
                --circle-gap: 10rem;
                --padding-block: 12rem;

                position: relative;

                display: grid;
                grid-column: 10/16;
                justify-self: center;

                margin-right: 6.4rem;
                padding-top: var(--padding-block);
                padding-bottom: calc(var(--padding-block) + var(--circle-size) - (var(--circle-gap) * 2));
                &:before {
                    content: 'VC';
                    @include text(h5);
                    color: var(--cl-orange);

                    position: absolute;
                    top: 50%;
                    left: 50%;
                    transform: translate(-50%, calc(-50% + var(--circle-gap) / 2));
                }
            }

            &-circle {
                grid-area: 1/1/2/2;
                @include size(var(--circle-size));
                border-radius: 50%;
                border: 1px dashed var(--cl-dm-disable);
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                transform-origin: center calc(var(--circle-size) - (var(--circle-gap) / 2));

                @for $i from 1 through 3 {
                    $rotation: calc(#{1 - $i} * 120deg);
                    &:nth-child(#{$i}) {
                        transform: rotate($rotation);
                        .about__intro-passion-circle-txt {
                            transform: rotate(calc($rotation * -1));
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
</style>